HTML/FormParser version 0.01
============================

This module can be used to parse HTML text for forms. Each type of tag that is
commonly found in a form (such as input, select, textarea etc) will trigger
callbacks provided at the application level.

The module inherits from HTML::Parser, which does all the grunt work. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  HTML::Parser

